Global Beta-Alanine Market Insights
Beta-Alanine Market size was valued at USD 0.58 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.02 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Beta-Alanine Market Overview
The global Beta-Alanine market is expected to reach USD 350 million by 2027, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 12.4% from 2020. This market growth is driven by the increasing demand for Beta-Alanine in the sports and fitness industry, where it is utilized as an ingredient in performance-enhancing supplements. Additionally, Beta-Alanine's application in various industries such as cosmetics and pharmaceuticals further propels its market value. With continuous innovation in product formulations and the growing health consciousness among consumers, Beta-Alanine's market is poised for significant expansion across various regions.

